LifeSensor.Description:
Senses and detects organic life up to a distnace of 2000 studs. Used mainly in programming, as is used in alien technology to hunt down organisms such as players.
Has a special programmable event called 'GetReading()' which returns a table of all organisms, with their positions and names.
Example:
{
	Player1 = Vector3.new(5, 5, 5);
}
